OL,3,CLeeds lose to Chelsea in FA Cup semis
OL,5,FThousands of Yorkshire fans made the
OL,6,Ftrip down to London to see Leeds
OL,7,FUnited play in the FA Cup semi-final.
OL,9,FIt is the first time they have reached
OL,10,Fthis stage in the competition for 39
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,FHowever, the Whites were narrowly
OL,14,Fbeaten by Chelsea FC - with the final
OL,15,Fscore 1-0.
OL,17,FChelsea dominated the ball in the
OL,18,Ffirst half, but Leeds had a number of
OL,19,Fchances which forced great saves from
OL,20,FBlues keeper Robert Sanchez.
OL,26,@|D@Vrp
