PN,36302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1777309554
OL,3,CLeeds lose to Chelsea in FA Cup semis
OL,5,FIn the second half, the Whites pushed
OL,6,Fhard for an equaliser, pinning Chelsea
OL,7,Fdeep in their own half, but they
OL,8,Ffailed to turn their pressure into
OL,9,Fgoals.
OL,11,FThough Leeds went in as underdogs,
OL,12,Fthey had been on a great run of form,
OL,13,Fhaving beaten Manchester United and
OL,14,Fdrawing away at Bournemouth in recent
OL,15,Fweeks.
OL,17,FMeanwhile, Chelsea had lost their last
OL,18,Ffive games in the Premier League
OL,19,Fwithout scoring.
