OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1777309554
OL,3,CLeeds lose to Chelsea in FA Cup semis
OL,5,FFor many fans, the match stirred
OL,6,Fmemories of the brutal 1970 FA Cup
OL,7,Ffinal.
OL,9,FBut the result means the next final
OL,10,Fwill see the Blues take on Manchester
OL,11,FCity, who overcame a spirited
OL,12,FSouthampton side the day before.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
